## Visual design source of truth

- **`doc/design-doc/`** — canonical product design spec (color, typography roles, spacing, motion, components, a11y, handoff). Start with `02-color-system.md`, `03-typography.md`, `04-spacing-grid-layout.md`, `07-motion.md`, `08a-/08b-/08c-components-*.md`, `10-page-anatomy-flows.md`, `11-accessibility.md`, `14-handoff-and-tokens.md`.
- **Implementation** — `app/globals.css` exposes `var(--color-*)`, `--radius-*`, `--shadow-*`, `--duration-*`, `--ease-*`, `--z-*`, `--site-header-height`, `--marquee-edge-fade`, plus typography utilities `.type-display-1`, `.type-display-2`, `.type-headline`, `.type-title`, `.type-subtitle`, `.type-body-l`, `.type-body`, `.type-caption`, `.type-eyebrow`, `.type-disclosure`. Marketing UI must use these instead of ad-hoc `text-[Npx]` ladders or stray hex.
- **Resolved spec values (implement; do not re-litigate):**
  - CTA labels: `text-base font-semibold` (16px).
  - `--color-cta-hover` is `#20bd5a`.
  - `--color-text-muted` is `#4b5563`; `--color-text-subtle` is `#6b7280`.
  - Marquee duration: `--duration-marquee` = 30s.
  - Form input radius: `--radius-input` (8px).
  - Hero accent span: `var(--color-brand)` on light surfaces, `var(--color-cta)` on dark band (per `03 §6.4`).
  - Marketing headings: `font-semibold` (sanctioned exception: stat numerals).
  - One `<h1>` per page. Home hero `.type-display-1`. Product hero `.type-display-2`. Section `<h2>` `.type-headline`. Card `<h3>` `.type-title`.
  - `PrimaryCta` / `PrimaryCtaAction` are the canonical CTA components (`/primary-cta`).

